    "body": "# Pull Request\n\n## Description\nThis PR introduces new, high-value content for October 2025, focusing on Edge AI in Healthcare and LLM Automation in Financial Services. It includes two new blog posts, two detailed case studies showcasing significant ROI, and a new service offering. The frontend has been updated to prominently advertise this new content via a dedicated banner and an updated content promo strip on the homepage, resolving previous merge conflicts in `app/page.tsx` to ensure a clean integration.\n\n## Type of Change\n- [ ] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n- [x] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\n- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to not work as expected)\n- [ ] Documentation update\n- [ ] Refactoring (no functional changes)\n- [ ] Performance improvement\n- [ ] Security fix\n\n## Testing\n- [x] I have tested this change locally\n- [ ] I have added tests for this change\n- [x] All existing tests pass\n- [x] I have tested the build process\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] My code follows the project's style guidelines\n- [x] I have performed a self-review of my code\n- [x] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\n- [x] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation\n- [x] My changes generate no new warnings\n- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works\n- [x] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes\n- [ ] Any dependent changes have been merged and published\n\n## Screenshots (if applicable)\nN/A\n\n## Additional Notes\nThe new content specifically includes:\n- **Blog Posts**:\n    - `ai-2025-oct-01-edge-ai-healthcare-revolution.md`\n    - `ai-2025-oct-01-financial-services-llm-automation.md`\n- **Case Studies**:\n    - `ai-2025-oct-01-healthcare-edge-ai-transformation-42-million-success.md`\n    - `ai-2025-oct-01-financial-services-llm-automation-87-million-success.md`\n- **Service Offering**:\n    - `october-2025-edge-ai-enterprise-transformation-services.md`\n\nThe homepage (`app/page.tsx`) was updated to include the `October2025NewContentBanner` and to refresh the content promo strip with links to these new resources.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-bd8a809e-f678-4842-9d2d-f7f42d82e5ec\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-bd8a809e-f678-4842-9d2d-f7f42d82e5ec\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\"></picture></a>\n\n",
