    "body": "# Pull Request\n\n## Description\nThis PR introduces two new pieces of content: a blog post on \"Cognitive Automation: The Enterprise Revolution of 2025\" and a case study on \"Healthcare AI Transformation: $124M Saved, 3.8M Patients Served Better.\" The application's routing has been updated to include these new pages, and the homepage now prominently features and advertises this content to enhance discoverability.\n\n## Type of Change\n- [ ] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n- [x] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\n- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to not work as expected)\n- [ ] Documentation update\n- [ ] Refactoring (no functional changes)\n- [ ] Performance improvement\n- [ ] Security fix\n\n## Testing\n- [x] I have tested this change locally\n- [ ] I have added tests for this change\n- [x] All existing tests pass\n- [ ] I have tested the build process\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] My code follows the project's style guidelines\n- [x] I have performed a self-review of my code\n- [x] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\n- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation\n- [x] My changes generate no new warnings\n- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works\n- [x] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes\n- [x] Any dependent changes have been merged and published\n\n## Screenshots (if applicable)\nN/A\n\n## Additional Notes\n*   **New Blog Post:** \"Cognitive Automation: The Enterprise Revolution of 2025\" has been added at `/blog/ai-2025-oct-cognitive-automation-enterprise-revolution`.\n*   **New Case Study:** \"Healthcare AI Transformation: $124M Saved, 3.8M Patients Served Better\" has been added at `/case-studies/healthcare-ai-transformation-2025`.\n*   The homepage (`/`) has been updated to feature these new content pieces in both the hero banner and the dedicated content highlight section.\n*   New routes for these pages have been added in `src/router.tsx`.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-c5fb5d72-fe46-4969-9155-9ffd37ef00c9\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-c5fb5d72-fe46-4969-9155-9ffd37ef00c9\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\"></picture></a>\n\n",
